From f47bf4bca6582fafea479bad3741aefbf281d492 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Caleb Dowling <cdowling@bndsrx.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 10:19:31 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add sig codes library with 88 pre-built codes and Rx
 form integration

- Add SigCode Prisma model with code, expansion, category, route, frequency fields
- Create sig_codes table in Supabase with 88 seeded pharmacy sig codes across 13 categories
  (common tablet/capsule, frequency, route, liquid, topical, ophthalmic, otic, inhalation,
   nasal, rectal, vaginal, injection, compound)
- Build sig codes management page at /prescriptions/sig-codes with CRUD, search, category
  filtering, active/inactive toggle, and usage tracking
- Create SigCodePicker component with autocomplete dropdown, keyboard navigation
  (Ctrl+Space or / to activate), and usage count tracking for popularity sorting
- Integrate SigCodePicker into new prescription form replacing plain textarea
- Add postinstall script for prisma generate to ensure Vercel builds work

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
